  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Kohlmais or Reiterkogel Austrian Twins</strong> are around 22m² - 26m² and sleep up to three (single sofa bed). These rooms have a bath or shower, seating area and balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Kohlmais or Reiterkogel Austrian Twins</strong> that are larger at around 30m² can sleep up to four (double sofa bed). These rooms have a bath or shower, seating area and balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Spielberg or Bernkogel Junior Suites</strong> are spacious at 35m². These suites can sleep up to four (double sofa bed) and are on request, so please call us to book.</p>
<p><strong>Kohlmais Single or Reiterkogel Single Rooms</strong> are around 22m². These rooms have a seating area and balcony and an additional single bed can sleep a child under 15 years old.</p>
